    metaDescription: "When is the best time for a Bosphorus cruise in Istanbul? Season-by-season guide covering weather, crowds, prices & what to expect. Plan your perfect cruise.",
    excerpt: "Planning a Bosphorus cruise? Learn the best season, month, and time of day for the perfect experience based on weather, crowds, and what you want to see.",
