    title: "Istanbul Transportation Guide for Tourists — Metro, Tram, Ferry & More",
    metaDescription: "Navigate Istanbul like a local. Complete guide to metro, tram, ferry, bus, taxi & Istanbulkart. Airport transfers, Bosphorus ferries, routes to attractions.",
    excerpt: "Istanbul's transport system is extensive and affordable. This guide covers everything from airport transfers to ferries, trams, and the essential Istanbulkart.",
